8
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,440
No.

9
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,079
I don't get it.

10
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,480
What's the use of these two cups?

11
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:22,320
The existence of these two cups itself

12
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:23,360
