33
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:06,200
Then he didn't take medicine for his heart condition.

34
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:09,680
Then what medicine did he take?

35
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,160
Sildenafil.

36
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,260
It's really possible.

37
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:17,040
The medicine Cheng Mo mentioned is called sildenafil,

38
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,500
commonly known as Viagra.

39
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,519
Theophylline and tannins in tea

40
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,959
will affect the efficacy of Viagra.

41
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:25,320
And an overdose of Viagra will overload the heart.

42
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:29,760
People with a history of heart disease are more prone to sudden heart failure.

43
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:32,680
Judging from my investigation of the scene at that time,

44
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:36,600
the victim's symptoms did look like he had taken Viagra.

45
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,360
He was physically weak,

46
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,520
