47
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,360
What a beast.

48
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,210
Captain Zhuang.

49
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:47,760
But this is just our speculation, right?

50
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:50,520
I didn't find any evidence at the scene.

51
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:53,970
Judging from the placement of the teacup,

52
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:54,890
the medicine

53
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,240
is here.

54
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:19,850
As expected.

55
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,930
There really is this medicine.

56
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,000
Shao.

57
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:29,740
I want a detailed autopsy report now.

58
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,060
This...

59
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:33,460
I'll take the blame for any problems.

60
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:38,640
We are one step closer to the truth.

61
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:46,240
Zhuang Lan.

62
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:49,170
