225
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:44,360
The duty of the police is to speak for the dead

226
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,400
and protect the rights of the living.

227
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,040
Right.

228
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:47,680
As long as

229
