233
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:56,280
Exactly.

234
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:56,680
Right.

235
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,240
The autopsy results

236
00:12:58,240 --> 00:13:01,160
